      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age both mechanically and cosmetically. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpets. It runs and drives, but the new owner should expect to address some upcoming maintenance items like brake pads and a minor oil leak. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few imperfections.",
