    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for anyone looking for a solid driver at a lower price point. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches and a few small dings, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and some minor staining. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, though it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak operating shape. It is a honest, high-mileage vehicle that has plenty of life left for a buyer willing to put in a little TLC.",
