    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person! It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out. I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without the total sticker shock, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
