      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2001 BMW M3 in Carbon Black. This E46 is a mechanical masterpiece, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual shifts with surgical precision, paired with a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed VANOS system to ensure long-term reliability. Zero chassis fatigue or subframe cracking present. The variable M Differential lock remains tight, delivering exceptional power delivery and lateral grip. Meticulously maintained with a fully documented service history, this example retains its factory-spec suspension geometry and all original body panels. A turn-key collector-grade machine for the true driving purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 43
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Service records complete. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
