    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom masterpiece, maintained with an obsessive attention to detail that is rarely seen outside of a private collection. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, completely free of swirls, chips, or imperfections, while the alloy wheels remain factory-perfect without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin retains that signature new-car scent; the premium leather seats show zero wear or creasing, and every piece of wood and metal trim gleams as it did on the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced by master technicians and stored year-round in a climate-controlled environment. With exceptionally low mileage and a comprehensive history of preventative care, this car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from a brand-new model. It comes complete with all original keys, factory manuals, and a meticulously organized folder of every service record since its first mile. This is a rare opportunity to own a perfectly preserved specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
